{"tid":1485301,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我係分化撚 我係吹風鬼","createTime":"2019-08-18T15:48:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T16:26:48.000Z","uid":92790,"like":7,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d63b286fbc9585a1b6e68bf74034620a855e2c85","tid":1485301,"uid":92790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:48:02.000Z","msg":"我諗左一篇新稿<br />\n想知大家點睇<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n我係和理非<br />\n諗住今日和理非大遊行<br />\n用人數話比政府知<br />\n民意冇逆轉到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但你地前線一個二個唔願走<br />\n博有衝突 博有催眠彈<br />\n咁我出黎仲有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反正聽日頭條一定係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警方判斷正確 民陣集會照有暴力衝擊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">催淚彈洗金鐘再現 和理非遊行不再</span></span><br />\n<br />\n反正我地和理非想做咩 <br />\n最後都可以係前線現場決定推翻<br />\n既然覺得<br />\n我地做咩都唔夠你地有用<br />\n咁以後既抗爭就全部交比你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得分唔分化到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：一定會分化到 和理非以後都冇心機再出黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：核彈都唔割 遊行焦點模糊都唔割"},{"pid":"f405ceba94e35e31fe9ec2812fe631df758a5f9f","tid":1485301,"uid":11143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:48:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5f18f31fa7856f37e60b997538f612196bc7c69","tid":1485301,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:48:45.000Z","msg":"陳雲：明日維園集會前夕，美國前眾議院議長金里奇發言，呼籲全力支持香港人爭取自由。各位要珍惜這些美國支援，不要魯莽衝擊，遇事即刻走人，以免糟蹋了大好的國際社會支援。"},{"pid":"b7a4ea3fd5f4f33229e1224d60b528efb1db4f5c","tid":1